channel.title: What would you like to see in new YouTube videos?
channel.description: I have a YouTube account which u can search up as “DJ La Rocca”. I was wondering what would my fans or people in the community like to see as a next YouTube video? I might do a voice over. (How to make a banger)? Idk that’s why I’m asking you guys :)
